column2: # Provide insights on the hybrid model's performance
"- This hybrid combines SVR (strong short-term accuracy) and LSTM (temporal memory of patterns).\n",
"- Ensemble smooths volatility and improves generalisation.\n",
"- Useful in dynamic markets where sequential dependencies and margin-based trends coexist.\n")
- This hybrid combines SVR (strong short-term accuracy) and LSTM (temporal memory of patterns).
